							&euro;)</h4>
						<span class="badge badge-info">{{ p.category.name }}</span>
						<p>{{ p.shortDescription }}</p>
						<a href="{{ path('product_show', {'category_slug': p.category.slug, 'slug': p.slug}) }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">DÃ©tails</a>
